Class DistDenseMatrix

  • x10.lang.Object
    • x10.matrix.Matrix
      • x10.matrix.dist.DistDenseMatrix

  • public class DistDenseMatrix
extends Matrix
    Declaration: DistDenseMatrix{this(:x10.matrix.dist.DistDenseMatrix).grid.M==this(:x10.matrix.dist.DistDenseMatrix).M, this(:x10.matrix.dist.DistDenseMatrix).grid.N==this(:x10.matrix.dist.DistDenseMatrix)., } extends x10.matrix.Matrix.
    This class provides distributed dense block matrix over all places.
Current implementation supports unique mapping only.


     A partitioning grid is used to map place id to the pair of row block id
and column block id in the 2D partition.
